--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.6.0 (2020-12-01)
F: Add plugin 'camptocamp-prometheus-alertmanager-datasource' by default

* Version 0.5.1 (2020-11-27)
B: Correct and improve Monit configuration file

* Version 0.5.0 (2020-11-24)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (grafana_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-11-14)
F: Install 'grafana-worldmap-panel' plugin by default

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-11-10)
F: Add option to configure Grafana plugins (grafana_plugins_(all|group|host))

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-11-10)
C: Rename Ansible role from 'grafana_upstream' to 'grafana'

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-09-03)
F: Initial release
